# This example repo gives several examples of `closeread' documents


## Getting started:

* Visit [the closeread dev guide](https://closeread.dev/guide/)
* In your TERMINAL of the HOME FOLDER, `run quarto add qmd-lab/closeread`


## Guide to these files: 

Each **folder** hosts a separate example. Within each folder, you will need to go into the terminal to enable closeread. This home folder features [scrollytelling-quarto](scrollytelling-quartro.qmd) as a basic example. 


Once you feel more comfortable, move on to the [minard example](minard/index.qmd). Finally, you can explore the [political candidates example](pop_cands/pop_cands.qmd)